  "text": "dependency collection failures, changes to unused props also trigger render  \n\n### Version\r\n3.2.21\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[sfc.vuejs.org/](https://sfc.vuejs.org/#)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\nOpen your browser's console\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\nThe `log` will only be executed once.\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\nThe `log`  is executed all the time.\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
